snippet.title: Panchayat Season 4 - Official Trailer | Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Panchayat Season 4 Official Trailer
Starring Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Sanvikaa, Durgesh Kumar, Sunita Rajwar, Ashok Pathak, Pankaj Jha

A TVF Creation
Created by: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Chandan Kumar
Directed by: Akshat Vijaywargiya, Deepak Kumar Mishra
Written by: Chandan Kumar
Executive Producers: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey

Official Release Date June 24, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Amidst the much-awaited village panchayat elections, Pradhan’s and Bhushan’s camps battle tooth and nail to maintain the upper hand. The future of everyone, including Abhishek, hangs in the balance.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: ENG vs WI | 3rd T20I | Cricket Highlights | West Indies Tour Of England | 10th June 2025
snippet.description:
England secured a dominant 37-run victory over West Indies in the 3rd T20I at Utilita Bowl, Southampton. Batting first, England posted a massive 248/3 in 20 overs, with Ben Duckett leading the charge with an explosive 84 off 46 balls. West Indies fought hard but fell short, managing 211/8 in their chase. With this win, England completed a 3-0 series sweep, asserting their dominance in the shortest format.

snippet.title: Abdul की बात सुनकर क्यों डर गया Jetha? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Full Movie
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

The watchman receives a tip from Jethalal, who instructs him to pay close attention to his house. Later, Sodhi makes the decision to pose as a burglar in order to test the watchman's skills. Tapu is doing karate while sprinting around the home. Daya devises innovative strategies to apprehend any intruders who might attempt to enter her home. Champaklal comforts Gogi, who is terrified of the robbers. Tapu and his companions agree that they must protect their community from these alleged robbers. To defeat these robbers, they devise a circuit training program. The robbers, meantime, enter the community disguised as repairmen.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 160-162
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTXtajBo1G2UEa_wE8BVSU7

snippet.title: Superman | Tickets on Sale Now
snippet.description:
On July 11, the entire world will look up. Get tickets now for #Superman - Only In Theaters and @IMAX 

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”), Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (“The Last of Us”) and editors William Hoy (“The Batman”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, “Superman,” which will be in theaters and IMAX® nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: मैंने काशीनाथ के आखों मे कातिया का काल देखा है - Bollywood Action Movie - Sunny Deol - Ghatak
snippet.description:
#b4ufilmy #bollywood #hindi #hindimovie #movie #action #thriller #sunnydeol #meenakshiseshadri

फिल्म का नाम: घातक
कलाकार: सनी देओल, मीनाक्षी शेषाद्रि, अमरीश पुरी और डैनी डेन्जोंगपा
निर्देशक: राजकुमार संतोषी 
म्यूजिक : आर. डी. बर्मन

Movie Name : Ghatak
Cast : Sunny Deol, Meenakshi Seshadri, Amrish Puri, and Danny Denzongpa
Director: Rajkumar Santoshi
Music: R. D. Burman

घातक :- 
काशी नाथ बनारस के रहने वाले दयालु पहलवान और शंभू नाथ के कर्तव्यनिष्ठ दत्तक पुत्र हैं। शंभू नाथ, जो तंबर पत्र से सम्मानित स्वतंत्रता सेनानी थे, शहर में एक सम्मानित और प्रतिष्ठित व्यक्ति हैं। काशी, शंभू के साथ, शंभू के इलाज के लिए मुंबई आता है और अपने भाई शिव नाथ के साथ रहता है। काशी कॉलोनी में गौरी से मिलती है और उसे पसंद करने लगती है। उसे पता चलता है कि कॉलोनी को अत्याचारी गैंगस्टर, कात्या और उसके छह भाइयों द्वारा आतंकित किया जा रहा है। काशी के आगमन से पहले, सचदेव नामक एक निवासी ने कात्या के खिलाफ विद्रोह शुरू करने की कोशिश की, लेकिन उसने उसे बेरहमी से मार डाला, जिससे सचदेव की पत्नी मालती पागल हो गई। कात्या और उसके भाई काशी के दुश्मन बन जाते हैं जब वह मालती के साथ मारपीट करने की प्रक्रिया में उनके गुंडों की पिटाई करता है।

Ghatak :-
Kashi Nath is a kind-hearted wrestler and the dutiful adopted son of Shambhu Nath, living in Banaras. Shambhu Nath, who was a freedom fighter awarded with the Tambra Patra, is an honourable and respectable man in town. Kashi, along with Shambhu, comes to Mumbai for medical treatment for Shambhu and stays with his brother, Shiv Nath. Kashi meets Gauri in the colony and starts liking her. He learns that the colony is being terrorized by the tyrannical gangster, Katya, along with his six brothers. Before Kashi's arrival, a resident named Sachdev tried to initiate a revolt against Katya, but got ruthlessly killed by him, thereby making Malti, Sachdev's wife, go mad. Katya and his brothers become enemies with Kashi when he beats up their goons in the process of roughing up Malti.

Click here to Subscribe : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCu5XOxGxsoKgHDrWc_qksQQ

Subscribe For More Videos : http://goo.gl/v9HBF9

- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls

snippet.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. This is the album version of the song, and my favourite song on the album. Hope you guys love it. Sapphire out now" - Ed x

Pre-order 'Play' out September 12: https://es.lnk.to/playID

localized.title: Ed Sheeran - Sapphire (Official Music Video)

Listen to 'Sapphire' now: https://es.lnk.to/sapphireID

"Sapphire was the first song I finished for Play that made me know where the album was heading. It's why I finished the recording process in Goa surrounded by some of the best musicians in India. It was an incredible creative process. I shot the music video with Liam Pethick and Nic Minns across my India tour earlier this year, we wanted to showcase the beauty and breadth of the country and its culture. The final jigsaw piece for me was getting @Official_ArijitSingh on the record, but it was a journey to get there and such an amazing day of music and family. Me and him have done a full Punjabi version of the song that will come out in the next few weeks, which has a lot more of him on it. Portugal emerged victorious in a pulsating Derby against Spain in the UEFA Nations League 2024–25 final at Munich’s Allianz Arena. After an intense 2-2 draw through regular and extra time, the match was decided by a dramatic penalty shootout, where Portugal kept their composure to secure the title. Captain Cristiano Ronaldo then lifted his third trophy for Portugal.

snippet.title: 900KM at 200km/h in the Rain on BMW R1250 GSA | Autobahn Madness with Supercars!@CherryVlogsCV
snippet.description:
Brussels to Prague on My BMW R1250 GSA | Autobahn Top Speed Test in the Rain! 🌧🏍💨

Join me on an epic ride from Brussels to Prague, with a scenic detour through Luxembourg and an adrenaline-pumping blast down the German Autobahn — where there’s NO speed limit! 🚀

I push my BMW R1250 GSA to its limits alongside high-speed cars, all while navigating wet, rainy conditions. How fast did the GSA really go? How did it handle in the rain? You'll have to watch the full video to find out!

👉 Subscribe for more real-world motorcycle adventures, travel vlogs, and honest riding experiences across Europe.

📍 Route: Brussels 🇧🇪 → Luxembourg 🇱🇺 → Autobahn 🇩🇪 → Prague 🇨🇿
🏍 Bike: BMW R1250 GSA
🌦 Weather: Rainy & wet — but that didn’t stop us!

📹 Sit back, gear up, and enjoy the ride!

#BMWR1250GSA #AutobahnSpeedTest #MotorcycleAdventure #BrusselsToPrague #RainRide #MotoVlog

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta

Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.title: Uppum  Mulakum 3 | Flowers | EP # 320
snippet.description:
'Uppum Mulakum' returns with its third season, continuing as one of Malayalam TV's longest-running sitcoms. This beloved show blends humor and emotion, depicting the trials and tribulations of a middle-class family. Balachandran and his family are back in action. Let's see what's next!!

ഉപ്പും മുളകും 3 | എല്ലാദിവസവും വൈകുന്നേരം 6.30 ന് ഫ്ളവേഴ്സിൽ

Episode 4421: Boss Se Mulaqat
------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak’s boss invites him home but not just for a casual visit. Troubled by the strange events his guest is facing, he’s thinking of asking Taarak for help. Will Taarak accept his request?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4421 | 11 June 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Vacation Glimpses | Eid with Family | Kerala Vlog
snippet.description:
Vacation vlogs are very special for me as those memories are to be cherished many many years later.
We are in kerala for a month and hoepfully shall try to vlog as much possible

localized.title: Vacation Glimpses | Eid with Family | Kerala Vlog
localized.description:
Vacation vlogs are very special for me as those memories are to be cherished many many years later.
We are in kerala for a month and hoepfully shall try to vlog as much possible

player.embedHtml: <iframe width="480" height="270" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/zsulSaiVFHw" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe>

ja.title: 休暇のひととき | 家族と過ごすイード | ケーララ州Vlog
ja.description:
休暇中のVlogは私にとってとても特別なものです。何年も経っても、その思い出は大切に残るからです。
私たちは1ヶ月間ケーララに滞在しているので、できるだけ多くのVlogを投稿したいと思っています。

de-DE.title: Urlaubseinblicke | Eid mit der Familie | Kerala Vlog
de-DE.description:
Urlaubs-Vlogs sind für mich etwas ganz Besonderes, da diese Erinnerungen auch noch viele Jahre später in Ehren gehalten werden.
Wir sind einen Monat in Kerala und werden hoffentlich versuchen, so viel wie möglich zu vloggen.

fr-FR.title: Aperçus de vacances | Aïd en famille | Vlog du Kerala
fr-FR.description: Les vlogs de vacances sont très précieux pour moi, car ces souvenirs resteront gravés dans ma mémoire de nombreuses années. Nous sommes au Kerala pour un mois et nous espérons faire autant de vlogs que possible.

id.title: Sekilas tentang Liburan | Idul Fitri bersama Keluarga | Vlog Kerala
id.description:
Vlog liburan sangat istimewa bagi saya karena kenangan itu akan selalu dikenang bertahun-tahun kemudian.
Kami berada di Kerala selama sebulan dan mudah-mudahan akan mencoba membuat vlog sebanyak mungkin

pt-BR.title: Vislumbres de Férias | Eid com a Família | Vlog de Kerala
pt-BR.description:
Os vlogs de férias são muito especiais para mim, pois essas memórias serão guardadas com carinho por muitos e muitos anos.
Estamos em Kerala por um mês e esperamos tentar vlogar o máximo possível.

it.title: Scorci di vacanza | Eid con la famiglia | Vlog del Kerala
it.description:
I vlog delle vacanze sono molto speciali per me, perché sono ricordi che custodirò gelosamente anche molti anni dopo.
Saremo in Kerala per un mese e spero di riuscire a fare vlog il più possibile.

hi.title: छुट्टियों की झलकियाँ | परिवार के साथ ईद | केरल व्लॉग
hi.description:
छुट्टियों के दौरान बनाए गए व्लॉग मेरे लिए बहुत खास होते हैं क्योंकि वे यादें कई सालों बाद भी संजोकर रखी जाती हैं।
हम एक महीने के लिए केरल में हैं और उम्मीद है कि जितना संभव हो सके उतना व्लॉग बनाने की कोशिश करेंगे।

es-US.title: Vistazos de vacaciones | Eid en familia | Vlog de Kerala
es-US.description:
Los vlogs de vacaciones son muy especiales para mí, ya que esos recuerdos se conservarán durante muchos años.
Estaremos en Kerala un mes y espero intentar vlogear todo lo que podamos.

🔥 White Hill Music Presents 🔥 Booster (Official Video) 🎧 | Ammy Virk | Rise & Thrive Album
Your favourite Ammy Virk is back with one of the most awaited Punjabi songs of 2025 – Booster 💥
An energetic, power-packed banger penned & composed by Kaptaan, with vibrant music by Geet, and mixed/mastered by Dense.

🎶 This isn’t just a track, it’s a Punjabi music adrenaline shot! Perfect for gym playlists, high-speed drives, or whenever you need that extra boost!

🎤 Lyrics that hit hard, vocals that dominate – this one's already turning into a fan-favourite anthem from Rise & Thrive.

Maalak goat jatt ne nawiyan ghost gaddiyan de

Gutt vich sarb loha te dhaun ch tunneya gaadar ni
Watermelon warga laal
Ni utto haathi argi chaal
Te khanda jatt ne ohi maal jo tappeya ae border ni

Ni caran chakkri wang ghumaunde gabhru gedi te
Gasoline te gijje tank laan te jatt kude
Ho kayi aar liter whisky te vi laa diye lakh kude
Marble nira luxury touch
Kothi te bulletproof aa kach
Aathne busy ho jandi shatt
Ni sade 7 kude

Kaddiyan dhaun ton fadke lekhan vicho tangiyan ni
Aa cheene chitte taila kariyan ne 3 rangiya ni
Ho ghodi kare fly jidda lambo laal kude
Jawani latt te dharke latt baithi jatt naal kude
Ho lande chidde te landiyan jeepan
4 ku landu je shehdan beefan
Tareeke naal nabedu tareekan
Main aounde saal kude

Exclusive leeda latta pehlan ee paaliye pinde te
Shonki rafal hustle te tasal de jatt bathinde de
Pair tan dharti te par naa teesi te rehnda ae
Je kaptaan nu dekhnai sir tan chakna painda ae
Most welcome je koi aawe
Jihne jana beshak jaawe
Sasta circle kithe banawe
Ni munda mehnga ae

Teri haan te jattiye meeh paadeage kookan da

snippet.title: Middle Class Ki Soch Ko Badalna Seekho | By Sandeep Maheshwari
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

snippet.description:
► Click here to Subscribe the channel : https://bit.ly/3HS054l 

100 सेकंड में कैसे कम्पनी को हैक होने से बचाएगा अभिषेक बच्चन - Om Jai Jagdish -  ज़बरदस्त बेस्ट सीन - Anil Kapoor, Abhishek Bachchan - Om Jai Jagdish - 

Witness the heartwarming story of brotherhood and family values in "Om Jai Jagadish." Released in 2002, this Hindi film beautifully portrays the lives of three brothers and their unwavering bond despite facing various trials and tribulations. When their father passes away, the eldest brother, Om, selflessly takes on the responsibility of caring for his younger siblings, Jai and Jagadish. As they navigate life's challenges, including financial difficulties and personal aspirations, their unity is tested. Will their strong familial love withstand the pressures of the outside world? Experience a captivating narrative filled with emotion, drama, and memorable performances from a stellar cast.

◾ Film : Om Jai Jagadish.
◾ Director : Anupam Kher.
◾ Producer : Vashu Bhagnani.
◾ Cast : Anil Kapoor, Fardeen Khan, Abhishek Bachchan, Mahima Chaudhry, Urmila Matondkar, Pooja Batra.

snippet.title: Husband-Wife aur Weekend | a Lifemates story | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In Weekend Ka Mahabharat, the battlefield isn't Kurukshetra — it's the living room! 🏠⚔️
Prashant and Sayali, your favorite desi couple, go head-to-head in the ultimate weekend showdown. Prashant dreams of a peaceful weekend with snacks and sleep, while Sayali is all set with plans to go out, explore, and make "memories." What starts as a casual discussion quickly turns into a hilarious war of logic, drama, and emotional blackmail! 😅❤️

This sketch is every couple ever — one wants Netflix, the other wants adventure. Who will win this Weekend Ka Mahabharat? Watch now to find out!

#WeekendKaMahabharat #CoupleComedy #WeekendPlansGoneWrong #RelatableSketch #DesiCoupleGoals #TakeABreak

Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai
Creative Producer- Ravindra Sarowar

Production Asst. - Gajanan Lokhande
Runner - Nilesh Korde

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu Motion Rao | Father & Son Comedy Blast | MCM Special Episode
snippet.description:
Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu  Motion Rao | Father & Son Comedy Blast | MCM Special Episode
When Madhu’s small mistake turns into his father's big “motion” disaster, the entire village gets involved in this hilarious chaos! 💊😂
In this special episode titled "Middle Class Motion Rao", witness the ultimate father-son comedy as Madhu unknowingly gives his father some tablets that were meant for someone else! 😬 What follows is a rollercoaster of funny events — from unstoppable loose motions to public embarrassment, from hiding behind bushes to hilarious reactions inside the bathroom! 🚽💥
🌾 Set against the backdrop of rural middle-class life in Vijayanagaram, this episode captures the true essence of family comedy where embarrassment, emotions, and entertainment go hand-in-hand. Madhu’s mother adds more spice to the drama with her one-liners and typical middle-class “concern,” while the villagers only make things worse with their nonstop gossip! 🙈😅
🎭 Whether it’s Madhu’s innocent face, his father’s uncontrollable situation, or the unexpected twist at the end — this episode will make you laugh till your stomach hurts (but hopefully not like Rao garu's)! 🧻🔥

snippet.title: Evaremanukuntunna - Saahus Prince | New Video Song 2025 #calvarytemple #EVRM #evarem @DrPSatishKumar
snippet.description:
Lyrics - Tune - Voice :  Bro.SAAHUS PRINCE
With Blessings Of Man of God :  Dr.P.Satish Kumar garu
Music : Bro.ANUP RUBENS
                
                               ఎవరేమనుకుంటున్నా నిన్ను ఆరాధిస్తున్నా 
పల్లవి : ఎవరేమనుకుంటున్నా నిన్ని ఆరాధిస్తున్నా 
             నేనేమైపోతున్న నిన్ను కీర్తిస్తూ ఉన్నా 
             నిరాశ నిస్పృహలోన నీవైపే చూసున్నా 
             ఈ లోకపు అలజడిలో నా ఒడి నీవేగా                         ॥2॥ 

1.          మదిలో మనశ్శాంతి లేక 
             మాటకి ఏదో మిగిలి ఉన్న 
             మతి వీడి ఉన్న నన్ను 
             మళ్లీ కలిసి మన్నించావే..... 
             నా కథలో..... ఓ మలుపే తెచ్చావే 
             నా గుండెలో గొప్ప మార్పే ఇచ్చావే.. 
             యేసయ్యా.. నాకున్నది నీవయ్యా.. 
              యేసయ్యా.. నీవుంటే చాలయ్యా..... 

2.           బ్రతుకు బాట బరువుకు ఉన్న 
               బయటికి ఒకలా బ్రతుకుతున్న 
               దరిలేని నన్ను చేరి – బ్రమ నుండి వేరు చేసావే   ॥2॥ 
               యేసయ్యా... నన్నే భరించావా... 
               యేసయ్యా... నాకై బలైయవా... 
                దోషినైనా.. నన్నే ప్రేమించావా..... 
               దరిలేని.. నన్ను నీ దరి చేర్చావా.....

               
#calvarytemplelive  #evrm  #evarem #depression #lonely #sad #failure #broken #youth #drsatishkumarsongs  #drsatishkumar  #calvarytemplehyderabad #saahusprince #telugunewsongs  #suhaasprince #2025 #calvarytemplesongs #newsongs  #drsatishkumarsongs #latestchristiansong  #calvarytemplesongs #hearttouchingsong  #teluguchristianmusic #instagood  #instadaily  #instalike  #viralreels  #viral  #trending  #trendingreels  #shalom #blessed #worship #songs #music #prince #love

Dr Satish Kumar is a widely respected Pastor, Author, International speaker and Humanitarian.
 His powerful preaching, visionary leadership and Integrity have earned him much respect and following not only in India but around the world.

He is known for his emphasis on strong moral values, compassion and commitment to biblical standard of living. Despite his vast following and influence, Dr Satish Kumar remains a humble Man of God, who loves people and is accessible to all.

His commitment to integrity, transparency, and authenticity in ministry and life has earned him much respect both in India and around the world.

His extraordinary vision, leadership capabilities and unwavering faith have resulted in him building the biggest Church in Asia with more than 400,000 members.

Dr Satish Kumar is also a globally recognized figure featuring widely on various international platforms.

He has been conferred the Doctor of Divinity degree from ‘The Dallas Baptist University’ and the ‘Mother Teresa’ award for his service to humanity. He is also the Honorary Board Member of ‘Museum of the Bible’ Washington and also a Board member of CGI International, founded by Dr. Paul Yongi Cho, of South Korea.

He has been widely recognized for his humanitarian work, particularly during the COVID-19 pandemic, where he organized hundreds of volunteers to deliver food kits to the needy and suffering. He has also been instrumental in various community service projects, such as free medical clinics, food distribution programs and retirement homes.

He is a much sought after international speaker, who passionately communicates God’s Word. His messages air on 300 different television programs each month in several Indian languages, reaching millions in India and around the world.

Calvary Temple Hyderabad was built in just 52 days, which is a remarkable achievement. It is now the biggest church in Asia with more than 400,000 members. The dynamic worship, diverse congregation, biblical teachings and supportive environment make it an amazing place to worship and fellowship. Calvary Bible college, Calvary hospital, and Calvary school are offshoots of Calvary Temple and provide much needed education and health care to all its members. Calvary Temple is beautifully built and is one of the major attractions in Hyderabad featuring in the ‘Top places to visit’ on Trip advisor and other travel portals. Hundreds of people visit Calvary Temple every day to enjoy the serenity and the admire the beautiful edifice. You are invited to visit and worship at Calvary Temple Hyderabad and experience Gods presence and listen to His Word.

Calvary Bible college, Calvary hospital, and Calvary school are offshoots of Calvary Temple and provide much needed education and health care to all its members. Calvary Temple is beautifully built and is one of the major attractions in Hyderabad featuring in the ‘Top places to visit’ on Trip advisor and other travel portals. Hundreds of people visit Calvary Temple every day to enjoy the serenity and the admire the beautiful edifice. You are invited to visit and worship at Calvary Temple Hyderabad and experience Gods presence and listen to His Word.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Garmi ki wajah se pareshan hue nattu kaka?! | FULL MOVIE | Part 1 | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the FULL MOVIE of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSk2_rPKNCDcjNAA8vaDN-E&si=rC5AotwLD2r3MHna

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
